content: COME live with me and be my Love, And we will all the pleasures prove, If these delights thy mind may move,Then live with me and be my Love.
headline: COME LIVE WITH ME AND BE MY LOVE

content: My sweetest Lesbia, let us live and love; If all would lead their lives in love like me, But fools do live and waster their little light
headline: LET US LIVE AND LOVE
